examples.en: I shall be partying tomorrow night.
He spent the weekend partying with his friends.
The students were partying all night before the exam.
He was all in after an evening of dancing and partying.
After a night spent partying, the fraternity brothers were all severely inebriated.
The partying neighbors kept up their raucous laughter half the night.
Proper food and sleep should overweigh all-night partying in your priorities.
